choices regarding use of your information 
top 
we want to provide you with meaningful choices regarding our marketing communications and you may choose to limit or opt out of certain communications from t mobile at any time while you may elect not to receive marketing information from us if you subscribe to our services or buy our products you will continue to receive invoices customer service and transactional notices and similar communications 
