services and functionality offered through certain devices are provided in conjunction with other entities as a result personal information from your devices may be uploaded and stored on their servers for instance blackberry® service is provided in conjunction with research in motion rim and personal information from your device is stored on the blackberry enterprise servers their specific terms and conditions terms of use and privacy polices apply to those services 
